    <item>
      <title>Swim season</title>
      <link>https://astro-alexis.github.io/blog/swim-season/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Jun 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://astro-alexis.github.io/blog/swim-season/</guid>
     
      <description>
        
            
                <img src="/blog/swim-season/swim.jpg"></img>
            
        

        &lt;p&gt;With the warm days, swim season is upon us in Stockholm! I went swimming every day since last Saturday, it is &lt;strong&gt;glorious&lt;/strong&gt;. The water in the sea was still quite cold, around 13-14 degrees. In &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brunnsviken&#34;&gt;Brunnsviken&lt;/a&gt; though, it is perfect at around 18-19 degrees !&lt;/p&gt;
  
</description>
    </item>
    
