      <description>
        
            
                <img src="/blog/kungsangslilja/kungsangslilja.jpg"></img>
            
        

        &lt;p&gt;A pretty picture today, with one of my favourite flower: &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fritillaria_meleagris&#34;&gt;kungsängslilja&lt;/a&gt; in Swedish (and a great name in French: &lt;em&gt;Fritillaire pintade&lt;/em&gt;). It is the official flower of Uppland province, which encompasses Uppsala.&lt;/p&gt;
  
